The Commonwealth Liberal Party merged with several Labor dissidents (including Billy Hughes) to form the <a2_0><b6_0>Nationalist Party of Australia<b6_0/><a2_0/> in <a3_0><b7_0>1917<b7_0/><a3_0/>.
